title: Modbox
description: Modbox is a VR sandbox where you can use mods to create game experiences and share them online. Go online to play multiplayer creations together in a variety of game modes - or create your own game worlds by piecing parts together.Select from a large selection of mods to choose content for your creationsOver 1000+ different building parts - with even more included in user created mods on the Steam WorkshopCheck out tutorials and our wiki at http://www.modboxgame.com/ on how to buildShare your
